      "text": "Oh, this is a technical issue, not a content/refusal issue. The chat input isn't working - they can't submit messages at all. That's a UI/technical problem.\n\nLet me think about what could cause this:\n1. Browser issue - cache, cookies, extensions\n2. Rate limiting or account issue\n3. Bug in the interface\n4. Network connectivity\n5. Browser extension conflict (especially ad blockers or privacy tools)\n6. Session expired\n7. Input field bug\n\nI should ask some quick diagnostic questions or suggest the obvious fixes.Oh, that's a straight-up technical issue, not Claude being difficult. Few quick things to try:\n\n1. **Hard refresh** - Cmd+Shift+R (Mac) or Ctrl+Shift+R (Windows)\n2. **Check if you're rate limited** - sometimes the input just dies when you hit limits\n3. **Try a different browser** - rules out extension conflicts\n4. **Clear cache/cookies** for claude.ai specifically\n5. **Check if it's a specific chat** - does a NEW conversation work?\n\nIf it's just that one chat that's broken, might be a corrupted conversation state. Sometimes super long chats or ones with heavy artifacts just... break.\n\nWhat browser are you on?",
